title: Wanted
subTitle: The police kill Shibu, an innocent man, after mistaking him to be his lookalike Raja, an assassin. To escape from the police, Raja starts living with Shibu's parents as their son.

title: Eagoler Chokh
subTitle: A senior police officer and his assistant investigate a young woman's murder. As the case unfolds, he learns more about human psychology and the intricacies of his own mind.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: With folded hands, Parvati pleads before Shiva to accept her solemn prayers, eventually taking a pledge to construct a huge Shiva linga.

title: Chalo Prem Kori
subTitle: A young man joins hands with a gangster and falls in love with his sister. However, things change when he locks horns with a rival gang leader.

title: Kartabya
subTitle: A bridegroom disagrees to marry due to the non-payment of dowry by the bride's father. In spite of his brother's request, he remains stubborn and decides to stop his wedding.

title: Sejo Bou
subTitle: A poor man falls in love with a girl belonging to a wealthy family. In an attempt to separate them, the man is sent abroad. However, the couple's destiny intervenes, striving to bring them together.

title: Khokababu
subTitle: Abir Roy falls in love with his employer's younger sister. His employer, however, happens to be a dangerous gangster and is overprotective of his sister.

title: Annadata
subTitle: Sankar's life changes when he gets taken in by a rich businessman. Years later, an opportunity arises for him to prove his loyalty to his adopted family.

title: Villain
subTitle: Riya meets Sneha on a flight back home and they strike up a conversation. Surprisingly, Sneha's fiance turns out to be a lookalike of Riya's boyfriend, leaving her in a state of shock.

title: Villain
subTitle: Riya meets Sneha on a flight back home and they strike up a conversation. Surprisingly, Sneha's fiance turns out to be a lookalike of Riya's boyfriend, leaving her in a state of shock.

title: Kaal Ratri
subTitle: Savitri, a poor girl, is gang-raped by local boys and later saved by the school principal. However, he is shocked to learn that his son is a part of the crime but nonetheless helps her get justice.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Mahadev assures his devotees about their safety under his watch, while Tarakasur remains adamant about abducting Parvati.

title: Agni Yudha
subTitle: A brother and sister duo share a loving relationship. However, things take a turn when the sister falls in love with a young man.

title: Mayer Badhan
subTitle: Sagar and Shipra, a happily married couple, had their baby unknowingly exchanged at the hospital with another couple's child.

title: Jiban Niye Khela
subTitle: In the distant village of Dharampur, Dr Subhankar Sanyal fights the bureaucracy and brings justice to the lives of his patients.

title: Mahaguru
subTitle: Rudra Sen, a brave officer and an encounter specialist, is killed in the line of duty by a gangster. However, things become complicated when his doppelganger decides to take his place and avenge him.

title: Bondhoo
subTitle: A devoted father stands up to obstacles and fights against all odds to win legal custody of his young son.

title: Challenge 2
subTitle: ACP Abhiraj Roy, who believes his father is dead, accepts the challenge to catch a dangerous mobster. He soon discovers the source of corruption in the political nexus and decides to end it.

title: Challenge 2
subTitle: ACP Abhiraj Roy, who believes his father is dead, accepts the challenge to catch a dangerous mobster. He soon discovers the source of corruption in the political nexus and decides to end it.

title: Saat Bhai Champa
subTitle: A princess is raised by a maidservant, unaware of her true lineage. However, when she learns of her stepmothers having killed her seven brothers, she vows to avenge their deaths and reclaim her right.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Overcome by Sati's memories, Lord Shiva expresses his inability to break the shivling, while Tarakasur plans to marry Parvati and take the place of Lord Shiva in the universe.

title: Hero No. 1
subTitle: A young man falls for a woman after she flees from her abusive husband. Later, as they work together to save orphans, their growing bond is tested by her past.

title: Madhur Milan
subTitle: Sunita, who hails from a rich family, is mesmerised by Gopal's music. Their interactions over time compel them to believe they are lovers from a previous life.

title: Maan Maryada
subTitle: Yogesh, a selfless man, takes care and raises his two step-brothers, a step-sister and an orphan boy. However, when things go south and he becomes bankrupt, his step-siblings abandon him.

title: Khoka 420
subTitle: Krish is the son of a rich man and is in love with Megha. However, things become complicated when Megha's best friend, Bhoomi, enters their lives and falls in love with Krish.

title: Ranakshetra
subTitle: When Santu protests against availability of drugs and gets murdered by a minister's son, his brother, Raja decides to seek justice on his own after his legal efforts go in vain.

title: MLA Phatakesto
subTitle: A notorious goon aspires to become a member of the Legislative Assembly and in an attempt to do so, he gives himself seven days.

title: Phande Poriya Boga Kande Re
subTitle: A light-hearted wedding turns tense when buried family rivalries threaten to explode, testing the resolve of a newly arrived son-in-law.
